Package com.poesys.db.dao.query

Interface Summary
IKeyQuerySql<T extends IDbDto> An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryByKey object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for an IDto.
IParameterizedCountSql<P extends IDbDto> An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryCount object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement that returns an integer count of a set of objects specified by a set of parameters defined in an IDto of type P
IParameterizedQuerySql<T extends IDbDto,P extends IDbDto> An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryListWithParameters object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs) specified by a set of parameters defined in a second DTO
IQueryByKey<T extends IDbDto> An interface for Command-pattern data access objects (DAOs) that query by a key within a data transfer object (DTO)
IQueryCount<P extends IDbDto> An interface for Command data access objects (DAOs) that query a count of some kind based on a set of parameters contained in an IDto of type P
IQueryList<T extends IDbDto> An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs)
IQueryListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends Collection<T>> An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs).
IQuerySql<T extends IDbDto> An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryList object to build a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs)
 

Class Summary
QueryByKey<T extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key.
QueryCacheByKey<T extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key including caching.
QueryCacheList<T extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching.
QueryCacheListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends Collection<T>> An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching.
QueryCount<P extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryCount interface that performs the basic count query given a parameter data transfer object (DTO) of type P
QueryList<T extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryList interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a SQL statement with no parameters.
QueryListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends Collection<T>> An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a parameterized SQL statement.
QueryMemcachedByKey<T extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key including caching in the distributed memcached server.
QueryMemcachedList<T extends IDbDto> An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching using the distributing caching system memcached.
QueryMemcachedListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends Collection<T>> An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching.
